definition: strip/item/article/clause (of law or treaty)/classifier for long thin things (ribbon, river, road, trousers etc)

sentences.english: Grid plow is applicable to different soil and has the function of crushing.
sentences.chinese: 柵條犁體，適用於不同土壤，具有碎土功能。

sentences.english: Any removable pedestrian flooring on deck to be of grating type.
sentences.chinese: 任何可移動的在甲板上的步行區必須帶柵條。

sentences.english: For lashing of containers a grating type walkway will be arranged between hatches.
sentences.chinese: 爲了綁紮集裝箱，艙口之間要安排柵條型過道。
